**Example of Real Benefit**

Suppose you want to build an image classifier.

Without PyTorch, you would need to manually handle:

- data representation
- matrix operations
- gradient calculations
- layer definitions
- weight updates
- GPU usage

With PyTorch, those pieces are already available, so you can focus on solving the problem instead of building the machinery.

